text.section:
A tax is hereby levied on each offender engaging in a taxable activity in this state. The tax shall be paid at the following rates:
One thousand dollars ($1,000) per plant, whether growing or detached from the soil, on each marijuana plant with foliation;
Three dollars and fifty cents ($3.50) on each gram, or portion thereof, of marijuana which has been detached from the plant on which it grew;
Two hundred dollars ($200) on each gram, or portion thereof, of controlled substances; and
Two thousand dollars ($2,000) on each fifty (50) dosage units, or portion thereof, of a controlled substance that is not sold by weight.
